subject: Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Automobile Racing
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick is guaranteed a spot in the Daytona 500 via a partnership with Tommy Baldwin Racing, which will officially field her No. 10 Chevrolet in all 10 of her Sprint Cup Series races this year.
